Casablanca,YvVMlidSQpI,UgxNjC24Kw4BBrA8qOV4AaABAg,,@jcd3869,"Thanks for this content. I watch this every trip to France to remind myself about romantic, egoic love vs. fundamental, genuine love. We can always look at the man in the mirror proudly when we honor the latter. Then even though we did it wanting nothing in return, more love comes to us as a result. 

