Rabat,el9PBqQg6zA,Ugw5uYxw_Th82dMAzmJ4AaABAg,,@LRPhotographer,"I've been to Morocco three times, and I've made it a point to go to the medina in Rabat every time, no matter where else in the country I traveled. But, the whole country leaves me homesick for it every time I return to the U.S. I hope to go back again someday soon and to finally be able to take my husband with me. The Rabat medina will definitely be on our itinerary. And, even being from the southern U.S., which is known for its hospitality, I can confidently (though somewhat sadly) say we've got nothing on the hospitality of Moroccans. Even visiting the very first time feels like going home. 🥰🥰🥰",2026-04-29T01:11:03Z,2026-04-29T01:11:03Z,1,False,0.0,2026-05-10T02:01:37.723122
