Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugzw0hdsOOdS-EeaQdx4AaABAg,,@IkeOzurumba,"i just got back from a vacation in Morocco (Marrakech and Essaouira), I cant stop thinking about it, I think Morocco might be my favorite place ive  traveled to so far. My biggest advice to people is to learn to simply ignore anyone who approaches you and tries to sell you something, offer you something, or assist you with something that you didnt ask them for. You simply have to. (and I do mean literally ignore them, dont pay them attention) Learn to do this and your time will be amazing! I really really loved this place. The people are so warm and inviting, the Medinas are so interesting and endlessly entertaining, the food, oh the food! Not everywhere is the best food (think tourist traps) but if you read up on some reviews you can really find some of the most amazing foods! I'm sitting here at home missing it all! Awesome video, helped me relive my awesome trip. Recently discovered you channel and love it.Using it to prep for new adventures! THanks!",2025-01-10T20:00:24Z,2025-01-10T20:01:55Z,27,False,4.0,2026-05-10T02:01:47.506390
