Tangier,_KHLnRCTXwk,Ugx3an6LKbeMG-1eSdp4AaABAg,,@artdirector9517,"Great 🙂👍 Morocco is safe just make your back bag on your chest in the crowded souks. Second thing barging, haggling is the national sport in Morocco so try to negotiate every price in the old souks without shame. Also you can see some beggars, 70 % of them are pro they can earn more than a bank manager. but if you are tired and you look for some chillout go to the city of the wind Essaouira city or Assillah city, or warzazet city. For Information the norrd of Morocco is a little cold in janury. In general Morocco is good for travel, rich of culture and safe. Life is not easier like in europe but he do the best of he can. Good travel enjoy every moment",2023-08-21T11:02:46Z,2023-08-21T11:02:46Z,13,False,7.0,2026-05-10T02:02:07.791766
