Tangier,wJhvcmFMpwY,UgzbYNj9p9pLY4XXxi94AaABAg.95N0hoQ2JXB9ZO3OC62l7q,UgzbYNj9p9pLY4XXxi94AaABAg,@rotadymaify,"@nathanlansford1882 80’s rock were the masters of musicianship. Big melody vocals and hooks, screaming guitar solos, big production and actually putting on a show for their fans. Great stage presence. Not like the bull shit that poisoned the music scene in the 90’s. Flannel shirts, greasy hair, singing about suicide, no melody to the music and no guitar solos. No wonder grunge only lasted a few years. It sucked.",2022-03-10T07:28:02Z,2022-03-10T07:28:02Z,8,True,,2026-05-10T02:02:14.059750
